Robo Mongo Installation Guide
==============================

#Download robongo from official site or from terminal
********wget https://download.robomongo.org/0.9.0/linux/robomongo-0.9.0-linux-x86_64-0786489.tar.gz

#Extract the gz file in a folder
********tar -xvzf robomongo-0.9.0-linux-x86_64-0786489.tar.gz

#Create a target directiory for installing robomongo
********sudo mkdir /usr/local/bin/robomongo

#Move the extracted directiory to the robomongo folder
********sudo mv  robomongo-0.9.0-linux-x86_64-0786489/* /usr/local/bin/robomongo

#Change directiory
********cd /usr/local/bin/robomongo/bin

#Change directory mode
********sudo chmod +x robomongo ## run command only if robomongo isn't excutable file
./robomongo
